text: Manolo Sanlúcar (born Manuel Muñoz Alcón, 24 November 1943 – 27 August 2022)Muere el guitarrista Manolo Sanlúcar was a Spanish flamenco composer and guitarist. He was seen as one of the most important flamenco composers. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Spanish guitarists Category:Spanish composers
